# Machine Learning Basics

## Types of Machine Learning
- Supervised Learning (labeled data)
- Unsupervised Learning (pattern discovery)
- Reinforcement Learning (decision-based learning)

## Common Models
- Linear Regression
- Logistic Regression
- Decision Trees
- K-Means Clustering

## Model Evaluation
- Accuracy
- Precision & Recall
- Confusion Matrix

## Workflow
1. Data collection
2. Data preprocessing
3. Model training
4. Evaluation
5. Optimization

## Key Takeaway
Machine learning is about finding patterns in data and making predictions based on those patterns.
